Perfect condition and LOVED the movie. Can't wait to give it to my daughter for her birthday!
I looked everywhere for this particular blue ray of "The Little Mermaid". Found it with ease here and ordered without any problems. Granddaughter was a happy girl.
this DVD will not play on my DVD player.  I need to return it!!
Great Grand Kids Loved it and use it daily.

This is and has been my favorite movie by Disney for decades.  I grew up watching all the Disney movies and still to this day watch them.  I purchased the DVD to add to my collection so that I can watch it whenever I want.  Its hard to pick a favorite character when you love them all but its a tie between Ariel and Ursula.  The music is also wonderful and you will be singing Ariel songs for days after watching this.  Disney you are amazing!  I will never stop watching Disney movies, ever.  At 33 my goal now Is to own them all.
thank you happy with a product
